<div class="col-md-6">
  <h2>Welcome&nbsp;</h2>
  <p>You may have not always felt heard and validated by the people in your life and it has become harder to share your whole self with others now. </p>
  <p>You may have been given messages that your emotional pain and physical pain are not valid and trusting your intuition and believing in yourself has gotten more difficult. </p>
  <h2>Our Work Together</h2>
  <p>I want to honor what your past self has gone through while creating a place of acceptance, validation and encouragement for your present self to thrive.</p>
  <p>I am passionate about helping you connect with the empowered you that feels just out of reach so you can move toward the life that you want.</p>
  </div>

<div class="col-md-6">
  <h4>Approaches I draw from:</h4>
  <ul>
  <li>Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing (EMDR)</li>
  <li>Compassion-Focused Therapy</li>
  <li>Attachment-Focused Therapy</li>
  <li>Person-Centered Therapy</li>
  </ul>
</div>
